          "isCorrect": false,
          "text": "4.5%"
        },
        {
          "feedback": "45% does not follow from the trial and paid counts. Dividing 90 paying customers by 2,000 visitors gives 4.5%, while dividing by 300 trials gives the requested 30%.",
          "isCorrect": false,
          "text": "45%"
        },
        {
          "feedback": "70% treats the users who did not pay as if they were conversions. Conversion counts the 90 paid users among the 300 trial users, which equals 30%.",
          "isCorrect": false,
          "text": "70%"
        }
      ]
    },
